/******************************************************************************                      
** Name		 : USP_IT_GetCalcEngineSecurityTypeCode                      
** Short Desc: To Get Account Payout Schedule
**                      
** Full Description:  To Get Security Type Code against Cusip
**            
**        
**                              
** Input Arguments: 
	 	@XmlInput xml

**         
** Sample Call     

EXEC USP_IT_GetCalcEngineSecurityTypeCode '<GiftDetailCollection><GiftDetail CustomerAccountNumber ="AMECK1" CUSIP="256219106" /></GiftDetailCollection>'
                 	
**                      
** Standard declarations                      
**       SET LOCK_TIMEOUT         30000   -- 30 seconds                      
**                       
** Created By: Saravanan P Muthu
** Company   : Kaspick & Company                      
** Project   : BackOffice Integration                      
